<div class="container">
    <div class="title sign-in">
      <p class="banner-text">Stolen Bicycle Registry</p>
    </div>
    <p class="lead sign-in">A free resource to register and track stolen bicycles.</p>
  <div class="row">

    <div class='col-md-4 home-div'>
      <div class="home-info lead well use" rel='<%= new_bicycle_path %>'>
        <h3 class="lead aboutbox">Register!</h3>
        <div class="hometext">
          <p>Maybe you just had your bike stolen.</p>

          <p>Maybe you're buying a used bike and want to run its serial number first.</p>

          <p>Maybe you work for a bike shop and want to know if that trade-in is hot.</p>
          <%= image_tag "bicycle.png", :class => "img-responsive twitterlogo", id: 'bicycle-icon', :alt => "Register!" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-4 home-div'>
      <div class="home-info lead well search" rel='<%= search_path %>'>
        
        <h3 class="lead aboutbox">Search</h3>
        <p>The Stolen Bicycle Registry allows users to search through a database, report stolen bicycles, and stay up-to-date on a stolen bike's status.</p>
        <br>
        <%= image_tag "magnifying_glass.png", :class => "img-responsive twitterlogo", id: 'search-icon', :alt => "Search!" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-4 home-div'>
      <div class="home-info lead well follow" rel='<%= twitter_path %>'>
        <h2 class="lead aboutbox">Follow</h2>
        <p>Twitter is a great tool when it comes to locating stolen bikes.</p>
        <p>Click to see if your city has its own Stolen Bike Registry Twitter feed.</p>
        <%= image_tag "twitter-bird.png", :class => "img-responsive twitterlogo", id: 'tweet-icon', :alt => "Follow us on Twitter!" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>